year%2C%20organisers%20said%20this%20week%2C%20after%20a%20fashion%20model%20and%20influencer%20claimed%20she%20had%20been%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Miss%20Universe%20Organization%20%26quot%3Bis%20currently%20undergoing%20a%20rigorous%20vetting%20process%20qualifying%20a%20potential%20candidate%20to%20be%20awarded%20the%20Saudi%20Arabia%20franchise%26quot%3B%2C%20Maria%20Jose%20Unda%2C%20the%20organisation's%20coordinator%20of%20international%20relations%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20have%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20National%20Director%20for%20Saudi%20Arabia%20very%2C%20very%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bpossible%26quot%3B%20for%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20have%20a%20contestant%20in%20place%20before%20the%20next%20edition%20of%20the%20competition%2C%20scheduled%20for%20September%20in%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20came%20after%20Saudi%20model%20Rumy%20al-Qahtani%20created%20a%20buzz%20online%20in%20late%20March%20when%20she%20posted%20to%20her%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Instagram%20followers%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bhonoured%26quot%3B%20to%20represent%20Saudi%20Arabia%20at%20Miss%20Universe%20at%20the%20upcoming%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20included%20pictures%20of%20Qahtani%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20native%20of%20Riyadh%2C%20in%20a%20sequined%20dress%20holding%20the%20green%20Saudi%20flag%20inscribed%20with%20the%20shahada%2C%20or%20Islamic%20creed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20week%20later%2C%20Miss%20Universe%20issued%20a%20statement%20referring%20to%20Qahtani's%20post%20as%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20misleading%26quot%3B%20and%20saying%20no%20selection%20process%20had%20been%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20Gulf%20kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFielding%20a%20Miss%20Universe%20candidate%2C%20if%20it%20happens%2C%20would%20mark%20another%20step%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20effort%20to%20soften%20its%20ultra-conservative%20image%20as%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%2C%20the%20de%20facto%20ruler%2C%20tries%20to%20lure%20tourists%20and%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20crude%20oil%20exporter%2C%20has%20long%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20repression%20of%20women%20because%20of%20former%20rules%20such%20as%20a%20ban%20on%20driving%20and%20a%20requirement%20to%20wear%20abaya%20robes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20those%20restrictions%20have%20been%20lifted%2C%20human%20rights%20activists%20say%20a%20personal%20status%20law%20that%20took%20effect%20in%202022%20still%20discriminates%20against%20women%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20matters%20concerning%20marriage%2C%20divorce%20and%20child-rearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20women%2C%20including%20prominent%20activists%2C%20have%20been%20rounded%20up%20in%20a%20wide-reaching%20campaign%20against%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20are%20two%20women%20who%20in%202022%20received%20decades-long%20prison%20sentences%20for%20social%20media%20posts%20critical%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Negative%20comments'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Riyadh%20home%20she%20shares%20with%20her%20mother%20and%20three%20sisters%2C%20Qahtani%20maintained%20she%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bnegotiations%26quot%3B%20about%20participation%20in%20Miss%20Universe%20but%20declined%20to%20provide%20further%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20contacted%20from%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20committee%20to%20represent%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20Negotiations%20started%20but%20it%20was%20during%20the%20month%20of%20Ramadan%20and%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20respond%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP%20in%20her%20first%20interview%20since%20her%20March%20Instagram%20post%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20negotiating%2C%20and%20hopefully%20it%20will%20result%20in%20a%20happy%20ending.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaria%20Jose%20Unda%2C%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20official%2C%20said%20the%20procedure%20calls%20for%20a%20national%20director%20to%20hold%20a%20Miss%20Universe%20Saudi%20Arabia%20pageant%20to%20choose%20a%20delegate%20to%20send%20to%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20ignore%20the%20reason%20why%20(Qahtani)%20announced%20her%20candidacy%2C%20but%20if%20she%20wants%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Saudi%20Arabia%20pageant%2C%20she%20will%20have%20to%20go%20through%20the%20same%20selection%20process%20as%20every%20other%20candidate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQahtani%20told%20AFP%20she%20had%20previously%20participated%20in%20various%20pageants%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Europe%20and%20posed%20with%20several%20sashes%20she%20said%20she%20obtained%20at%20the%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20described%20fielding%20a%20host%20of%20unexpected%20questions%20about%20Saudi%20Arabia%20during%20her%20bid%20to%20take%20the%20beauty%20pageant%20world%20by%20storm%2C%20including%20one%20from%20a%20fellow%20contestant%20in%20Europe%20who%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20she%20kept%20barrels%20of%20crude%20oil%20stored%20in%20her%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20while%20she%20has%20tried%20to%20manage%20the%20potential%20backlash%20back%20home%2C%20including%20from%20more%20conservative%20Saudis%20who%20object%20to%20her%20clothing%20or%20her%20decision%20to%20pose%20on%20Instagram%20last%20year%20wrapped%20in%20the%20Saudi%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20some%20negative%20comments%20about%20the%20way%20I%20dress%20and%20when%20I%20pictured%20myself%20with%20the%20flag%20wearing%20what%20people%20considered%20immodest%20clothing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20though%2C%20that%20she%20had%20no%20regrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20sports%20supporters%20picture%20themselves%20with%20the%20flag%20the%20same%20way%20I%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20beauty%20pageants%20also%2C%20each%20girl%20carries%20her%20own%20country's%20flag%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20mean%20anything%20offensive%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFawzia%20Ayed%2C%20Rumy's%20mother%2C%20told%20AFP%20that%20she%20hoped%20her%20daughter%20would%20persevere%20despite%20the%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20tell%20her%20to%20carry%20on%2C%20and%20that%20she%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20for%20a%20Saudi%20girl.%20Before%2C%20(society)%20was%20closed%20and%20strict%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRumy%20has%20encouraged%20a%20lot%20of%20girls.%20I%20see%20that%20many%20contact%20her%20and%20ask%20her%20how%20she%20has%20reached%20this%20level%2C%20and%20that%20they%20would%20like%20also%20to%20participate.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714104600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fjcgfn3s8_rumy-alqahtani_625x300_26_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-could-get-its-first-ever-miss-universe-contestant-this-year-5525985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saudi%20Arabia%20could%20have%20its%20first%20Miss%20Universe%20contestant%20this%20year%2C%20organisers%20said%20this%20week%2C%20after%20a%20fashion%20model%20and%20influencer%20claimed%20she%20had%20been%20selected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-could-get-its-first-ever-miss-universe-contestant-this-year-5525985%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-could-get-its-first-ever-miss-universe-contestant-this-year-5525985%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F