having%20a%20baby%20in%20Germany%20but%20has%20struggled%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20was%20impressed%20with%20the%20postpartum%20care%20and%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20going%20back%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-moved-from-detroit-to-berlin-covid-19-europe-visa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20Berlin%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20married%20and%20have%20a%20baby.%20I%20moved%20at%2029%20after%20visiting%20some%20friends.%20I%20had%20gotten%20the%20sense%20that%20if%20I%20didn't%20at%20least%20try%20to%20live%20in%20this%20city%2C%20which%20felt%20so%20much%20calmer%2C%20greener%2C%20and%20yet%20more%20alive%20than%20New%20York%2C%20I'd%20regret%20it.%20My%20cat%20and%20I%20arrived%20three%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fberlin-germany-things-to-see-parks-canals-musicians-art-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBerlin%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20still%20called%20%26quot%3Bpoor%2C%20but%20sexy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20twenty-somethings%20traveled%20to%20spend%20entire%20weekends%20in%20the%20city's%20techno%20clubs%20and%20live%20on%20the%20cheap%20in%20what%20used%20to%20be%20one%20of%20Europe's%20most%20affordable%20capitals.%20Even%20these%20days%2C%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Berlin%20is%2035%25%20less%20expensive%20than%20New%20York%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.numbeo.com%2Fcost-of-living%2Fin%2FBerlin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENumbeo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20expect%20to%20partner%20up%20and%20settle%20down%2C%20but%20pleasantly%2C%20that's%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20married%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-germany-relocation-american-move-disappointing-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGermany%3C%2Fa%