nters%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20in%20short%20supply%2C%20according%20to%20local%20news%20channel%20RBB24.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20became%20clear%20when%20I%20was%20just%20seven%20weeks%20into%20my%20pregnancy%20and%20at%20the%20gynecologist.%20She%20asked%20me%20if%20I'd%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20midwife.%20I%20hadn't.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20then%20you're%20already%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20doctor%20sighed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20I%20set%20an%20alarm%20and%20started%20calling%20the%20hospital%20that%20had%20been%20recommended.%20To%20register%20there%2C%20the%20hospital%20required%20expecting%20parents%20to%20call%20at%20exactly%2012%20weeks%20plus%20one%20day%20into%20pregnancy%20%E2%80%94%20try%20a%20day%20later%2C%20and%20they'd%20be%20full.%20Around%2010%20calls%20in%2C%20I%20got%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20months%20after%20that%2C%20we%20took%20a%20stab%20at%20the%20Kita%20Navigator%2C%20an%20online%20system%20aimed%20at%20helping%20parents%20find%20and%20contact%20daycares.%20Landing%20a%20Kita%20spot%20in%20Berlin%20is%20notoriously%20difficult%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bertelsmann-stiftung.de%2Fde%2Fthemen%2Faktuelle-meldungen%2F2022%2Foktober%2F2023-fehlen-in-deutschland-rund-384000-kita-plaetze%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20research%20foundation%20Bertelsmann%20Stiftung%2C%20the%20city%20is%20short%20around%2017%2C000%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20heard%20parents-to-be%20should%20get%20on%20waiting%20lists%20while%20still%20expecting%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20securing%20a%20place%20for%20an%20unborn%20child%20once%20they%20turned%20a%20year%20old.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20%E2%80%94%20mystified%20as%20to%20how%20to%20enter%20the%20name%20and%20birthdate%20of%20a%20baby%20still%20in%20utero%20%E2%80%94%20quickly%20gave%20up%20on%20attempting%20to%20navigate%20the%20unnavigable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkita-navigator.berlin.de%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKita%20Navigator%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThen%20came%20the%20flurry%20of%20bureaucracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20son's%20German%20birth%20certificate%2C%20my%20own%20US%20birth%20certificate%20needed%20an%20apostille%2C%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20authentication%20that%20this%20official%20document%20is%20indeed%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20baby's%20US%20citizenship%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20do%20a%20Consular%20Report%20of%20a%20Birth%20Abroad%20at%20the%20embassy.%20Off%20I%20went%20on%20an%20archaeological%20dig%20through%20our%20apartment%20for%20documentation%20to%20prove%20I'd%20previously%20lived%20in%20the%20US%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20as%20there's%20a%20residency%20requirement%20in%20order%20to%20pass%20on%20citizenship.%20Laid%20out%20end-to-end%2C%20everything%20we%20needed%20for%20the%20CRBA%20covered%20our%20bedroom%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20apply%20for%20Kindergeld%2C%20a%20monthly%20child%20subsidy%2C%20and%20Elterngeld%2C%20parental%20leave%20pay%2C%20there%20were%20paper%20applications%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20physically%20mailed%20off%20to%20various%20overburdened%20Berlin%20administrative%20offices.%20All%20I%20remember%20is%20running%20on%20about%20five%20hours%20of%20broken%20sleep%20per%20night%2C%20handing%20the%20baby%20off%20to%20my%20visiting%20mother-in-law%20in%20between%20nursing%20sessions%2C%20and%20tackling%20a%20pile%20of%20paperwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222997%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Toddler%20standing%20near%20playground%20with%20his%20hands%20out%20in%20the%20air%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6629cecf23b29110d302cdce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222759%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20that%20Berlin%20is%20filled%20with%20playgrounds%20and%20her%20toddler%20always%20wants%20to%20stop%20and%20play.%3Cp%3ESusannah%20Edelbaum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20thrilled%20to%20be%20raising%20a%20toddler%20in%20Berlin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20late%20start%2C%20I%20found%20a%20midwife.%20The%20postpartum%20care%20she%20offered%20me%20and%20our%20newborn%20was%20excellent%2C%20and%20I%20wish%20it%20were%20standard%20everywhere.%20Besides%20weighing%20the%20baby%2C%20checking%20that%20breastfeeding%20was%20going%20well%2C%20cleaning%20his%20umbilical%20cord%20stump%2C%20and%20doing%20the%20first%20bath%20with%20us%2C%20she%20gave%20me%20week-by-week%20worksheets%20with%20gentle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fpelvic-floor-excercises%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epelvic%20floor%20exercises%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20wound%20up%20translating%20for%20my%20friend%20in%20the%20US%2C%20who'd%20given%20birth%20the%20day%20before%20me%20and%20been%20given%20nothing%20of%20the%20sort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Kita%2C%20when%20my%20son%20was%20a%20few%20months%20old%2C%20I%20walked%20him%20around%20our%20neighborhood%20for%2090%20minutes%20while%20he%20napped%20and%20I%20wrote%20down%20the%20contact%20information%20posted%20in%20the%20window%20of%20every%20day%20care%20we%20passed%2C%20then%20emailed%20them%20individually.%20That%20worked.%20Now%20a%20toddler%2C%20he%20loves%20his%20Kita.%20It%20took%20around%20thirty%20waitlists%20to%20get%20offered%20a%20single%20spot%2C%20but%20all%20you%20need%20is%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20later%20learned%20that%20other%20expecting%20parents%2C%20particularly%20non-German%20speakers%2C%20pay%20self-styled%20experts%20to%20get%20certain%20tasks%20done%2C%20like%20applying%20for%20parental%20leave%20pay%20and%20navigating%20the%20Kita%20system.%20As%20a%20German-speaking%20household%2C%20we%20didn't%20go%20down%20this%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaken%20individually%2C%20no%20one%20task%20here%20is%20that%20difficult%2C%20it%20just%20felt%20like%20a%20lot%20altogether%2C%20lurching%20from%20one%20form%20to%20waitlist%20to%20the%20next%2C%20all%20while%20exhausted%20from%20pregnancy%20and%20the%20newborn%20months.%20But%20hey%2C%20the%20countervailing%20force%20of%20a%20safety%20net%20is%20a%20bureaucracy%20required%20to%20administer%20it.%20And%20I%20can%20hardly%20complain%20that%20the%20city's%20administrative%20offices%20are%20overburdened.%20People%20keep%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F13-things-that-surprised-a-londoner-in-berlin-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBerlin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I'm%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20understands%20everything%20he%20hears%20in%20both%20German%20and%20English.%20Getting%20around%20this%20city%2C%20where%20the%20public%20transit%20elevators%20work%20around%2080%25%20of%20the%20time%20and%20mostly%20don't%20smell%20like%20urine%2C%20is%20way%20better%20than%20anyone%20can%20say%20for%20New%20York's%20subway%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20biggest%20problem%20these%20days%20is%20the%20most%20non-problem%20a%20parent%20can%20have%3A%20Berlin%20has%20too%20many%20playgrounds.%20It's%20impossible%20to%20find%20a%20route%20anywhere%20from%20our%20apartment%20where%20we%20won't%20pass%20one%2C%20and%20our%20son%20always%20wants%20to%20stop%20and%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-in-berlin-giving-birth-maternity-care-raising-child-germany-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714090442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a190310dfcda4096320d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-in-berlin-giving-birth-maternity-care-raising-child-germany-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20millennial%20who%20moved%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Berlin%20for%20the%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20wasn't%20planning%20to%20have%20a%20