%20automatic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20a%20large%20litter%20box%20that's%20also%20hands-off%2C%20Whisker's%20Litter-Robot%204%20is%20your%20best%20bet%20and%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-self-cleaning-litter-boxes%5C%22%3Ebest%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20automatic%20litter%20box%20ensures%20your%20cats%20always%20have%20a%20clean%20box%20to%20use%2C%20which%20is%20important%20because%20cats%20are%20very%20fastidious%20about%20cleanliness%2C%20DeVoss%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Litter-Robot%204%20doesn't%20just%20automatically%20sense%20waste%20and%20tumble%20it%20into%20an%20odor-locking%20drawer.%20It%20also%20provides%20plenty%20of%20space%20for%20your%20cat%20to%20feel%20at%20ease%2C%20starting%20with%20a%20circular%20entry%2016%20inches%20in%20diameter.%20The%20interior%20globe%20measures%20a%20roomy%2015.75%20by%2015.75%20inches.%20The%20app%20will%20notify%20you%20when%20to%20empty%20the%20waste%20drawer%2C%20which%20may%20be%20every%20few%20weeks%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20cats%20and%20litter%20boxes.%20The%20brand%20also%20recommends%20deep%20cleaning%20the%20globe%20every%20one%20to%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20multi-cat%20household%2C%20Whisker%20has%20remained%20a%20trusted%20brand%20since%20the%20days%20of%20Litter-Robot%202%2C%20and%20we%20consider%20it%20well%20worth%20the%20sizable%20investment.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20you%20(or%20your%20cats)%20aren't%20happy%20with%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%2C%20you%20can%20return%20it%20within%2090%20days.%20You%20will%2C%20however%2C%20need%20to%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20shipping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fwhisker-litter-robot-4-review%5C%22%3EWhisker%20Litter-Robot%204%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20with%20high%20sides%5C%22%3EBest%20with%20high%20sides%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20the%20right%20litter%20box%20for%20your%20cat%2C%20their%20underlying%20health%20conditions%20matter.%20For%20example%2C%20conditions%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Furinary-tract-infection-in-cats%5C%22%3Eurinary%20tract%20infections%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20kidney%20disease%20can%20increase%20urine%20output.%20In%20addition%20to%20getting%20veterinary%20care%20for%20your%20cat%2C%20you'll%20also%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20there's%20always%20enough%20litter%20in%20the%20pan%20to%20quickly%20soak%20up%20the%20urine%20so%20it%20doesn't%20pool.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BGoldilocks%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20then%2C%20may%20be%20one%20that%20has%20high%20sides%2C%20a%20deep%20base%20for%20holding%20litter%2C%20and%20an%20entry%20low%20enough%20for%20small%20kittens%20or%20cats%20with%20mobility%20issues.%20Quandt's%20recommendation%20of%20the%20NVR%20Miss%20Litterbox%20fits%20the%20bill.%20He%20says%20he%20has%20two%20NVR%20Miss%20Litterboxes%20and%20especially%20likes%20that%20the%2011.2-inch%20walls%20shield%20the%20spray%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20shooter.%26quot%3B%20The%20interior%20of%20this%20box%20measures%20a%20spacious%2021.5%20by%2015.5%20inches.%20The%20box's%20entry%20height%20of%205.6%20inches%20will%20work%20for%20most%20cats%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20ideal%20for%20seniors%20with%20arthritis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20round%5C%22%3EBest%20round%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECircular%20litter%20pans%20are%20said%20to%20be%20ergonomically%20designed%20for%20cats%2C%20who%20tend%20to%20move%20in%20a%20circular%20motion%20when%20using%20the%20litter%20box.%20While%20DeVoss%20says%20there's%20no%20evidence%20cats%20prefer%20a%20circle%20litter%20pan%20over%20a%20box%2C%20reviewers%20still%20rave%20about%20the%20Boxscoop%20Curve%20XL.%20A%20cat%20dad%20engineer%20who's%20passionate%20about%20both%20efficiency%20and%20clean%20cat%20paws%20designed%20this%20round%20pan.%20It's%20made%20of%20durable%20BPA-free%20polypropylene%20plastic%20and%20has%20a%2020.5-inch%20exterior%20diameter%20at%20its%20base%20and%20an%20interior%20height%20of%2014.1%20inches%20at%20its%20tallest%20point%20(it%20tapers%20toward%20the%20front).%20The%20box%20also%20features%20a%20unique%20stepping%20pad%20in%20the%20center%20so%20your%20cat%20can%20enter%20without%20coming%20into%20contact%20with%20clumps%20of%20waste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20all%20cats%20access%20the%20entry%2C%20which%20is%209.5%20inches%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20Boxscoop%20provides%20an%20easy-access%20step.%20The%20step%20does%20double%20duty%20to%20help%20reduce%20litter%20tracking%20as%20your%20cat%20leaves%20the%20box.%20The%20included%20scoop%20is%20tailored%20to%20fit%20the%20contours%20of%20the%20bottom%20and%20sides%20of%20the%20litter%20channel.%20This%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20remove%20waste%20with%20just%20one%20swift%2C%20circular%20motion%20around%20the%20pan.%20Any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-litter%5C%22%3Eclumping%20litter%3C%2Fa%3E%20works%20for%20the%20Boxscoop%20Curve.%20You%20can%20also%20purchase%20this%20pan%20in%20a%20top-entry%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Boxscoop%20Curve%20is%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20round%20litter%20pans%2C%20we%20consider%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flesslitterearth.com%2Fproducts%2Fless-litter-box-l-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELess%20Litter%20Box%20L-6%3C%2Fa%3E%20worth%20a%20mention.%20This%20stainless%20steel%20round%20litter%20pan%20has%20a%2023.75%20inch%20diameter%20and%20a%20height%20of%2019.75%20inches.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20hefty%20price%20tag%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20%24450%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20brand%20says%20it%20lasts%20a%20lifetime.%20Since%20our%20experts%20recommend%20replacing%20plastic%20litter%20boxes%20roughly%20every%20six%20months%2C%20you%20may%20find%20this%20one-time%20purchase%20a%20wise%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20large%20litter%20box%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20input%20from%20our%20experts%2C%20research%2C%20and%20personal%20experience%2C%20we%20recommend%20considering%20these%20essential%20features%20when%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20large%20litter%20box%20for%20your%20cat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Because%20every%20cat%20is%20a%20different%20size%2C%20our%20experts%20say%20there's%20no%20standard%20litter%20box%20that%20suits%20every%20cat.%20Instead%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20box%20at%20least%201.5%20times%20the%20length%20of%20your%20cat%2C%20measured%20from%20their%20nose%20to%20their%20tail.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20kittens%20will%20need%20a%20low%20entry%20and%20a%20larger%20box%20as%20they%20grow.%20The%20largest%20litter%20box%20should%20work%20for%20cats%20of%20all%20ages%20and%20mobility%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessibility%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20senior%20cat%2C%20kitten%2C%20or%20feline%20with%20special%20mobility%20needs%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20choose%20litter%20boxes%20with%20low-to-the-ground%20entryways.%20The%20ideal%20entry%20height%20can%20vary%20from%20cat%20to%20cat%2C%20but%20aim%20for%20a%20box%20your%20cat%20can%20easily%20step%20into.%20To%20accommodate%20cats%20with%20mobility%20limitations%2C%20we%20chose%20litter%20boxes%20with%20low%20entrances%20or%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Our%20experts%20recommend%20open%20litter%20boxes%20that%20provide%20cats%20with%20unobstructed%20views%20and%20quick%20escape%20routes.%20If%20you%20prefer%20a%20covered%20or%20top-entry%20box%2C%20opt%20for%20one%20with%20ventilation%2C%20odor%20control%2C%20and%20multiple%20entrances.%20You%20can%20also%20disguise%20an%20open%20litter%20box%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-litter-box-furniture%5C%22%3Ebest%20cat%20litter%20box%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20most%20common%20materials%20for%20at-home%20litter%20boxes%20include%20plastic%20and%20metal.%20While%20plastic%20litter%20boxes%20are%20readily%20available%20and%20cost-effective%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20replace%20them%20at%20the%20first%20sign%20of%20scratch%20marks%20%E2%80%94%20or%20about%20every%20six%20months%2C%20according%20to%20our%20experts.%20Metal%20litter%20boxes%20tend%20to%20cost%20more%20upfront%20but%20have%20a%20longer%20use%20life%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you%20don't%20mind%20the%20sound%20of%20cat%20nails%20on%20metal.%20We%20included%20both%20metal%20and%20plastic%20large%20litter%20box%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20cleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20experts%20say%20litter%20boxes%20should%20be%20scooped%20daily%20and%20deep%20cleaned%20with%20soap%20and%20water%20every%20four%20to%20six%20weeks.%20To%20come%20up%20with%20our%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20large%20litter%20boxes%2C%20we%20considered%20the%20ease%20of%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20experts%20recommend%20having%20one%20litter%20box%20per%20cat%2C%20plus%20one%20extra.%20Since%20buying%20multiple%20litter%20boxes%20can%20add%20up%20quickly%2C%20we%20included%20litter%20boxes%20at%20a%20range%20of%20price%20points%2C%20including%20a%20DIY%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20large%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20more%20guidance%20on%20choosing%20the%20largest%20litter%20box%20that%20works%20best%20for%20your%20cat%2C%20we%20consulted%20three%20experts%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Denise%20Johnson%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffearfreepets.com%2Fresources%2Fdirectory%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFear%20Free%20certified%3C%2Fa%3E%20veterinarian%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiaabc.org%2Fen%2Fcredentials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecat%20behavior%20consultant%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CCBC)%20at%20IndeVets%20who%20specializes%20in%20behavioral%20health%20and%20low-stress%20handling.%20Johnson%20helped%20us%20understand%20the%20role%20a%20cat's%20age%20and%20health%20conditions%20play%20in%20choosing%20the%20most%20appropriate%20litter%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolly%20DeVoss%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.animaledu.com%2FPrograms%2FFeline-Training-Behavior%3Fd%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecertified%20feline%20training%20and%20behavior%20specialist%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CFTBS)%2C%20CCBC%2C%20and%20Fear%20Free%20certified%20trainer%20who%20specializes%20in%20using%20positive%20reinforcement%20to%20modify%20and%20prevent%20unwanted%20behaviors%20in%20cats.%20She%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20owner%20of%20Cat%20Behavior%20Solutions.%20DeVoss%20helped%20us%20understand%20what%20features%20to%20look%20for%20in%20litter%20boxes%2C%20including%20the%20size%2C%20material%2C%20and%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Quandt%2C%20CFTBS%20and%20founder%20and%20owner%20of%20Cat%20Behavior%20Help%2C%20has%20over%2020%20years%20of%20experience%20working%20with%20cats.%20His%20expertise%20lies%20in%20the%20understanding%20of%20feline%20behavior%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20a%20cat's%20evolution%20and%20adaptation%20to%20life%20with%20humans.%20Quandt%20helped%20us%20understand%20what%20features%20make%20a%20litter%20box%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ELarge%20litter%20box%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20size%20is%20an%20extra-large%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20our%20experts%2C%20no%20single%20extra-large%20litter%20box%20works%20for%20all%20cats%2C%20as%20each%20cat%20has%20a%20unique%20size.%20Instead%2C%20they%20suggest%20selecting%20a%20litter%20box%201.5%20times%20the%20length%20of%20your%20cat%20from%20nose%20to%20tail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20bigger%20cats%20need%20bigger%20litter%20boxes%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20larger%20the%20cat%2C%20the%20larger%20the%20box%20should%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Quandt%20says.%20As%20a%20general%20rule%20of%20thumb%2C%20your%20cat%20should%20be%20able%20to%20enter%20the%20box%20and%20turn%20around%20without%20any%20body%20part%20touching%20the%20sides.%20If%20they%20can't%20turn%20around%20comfortably%20inside%20the%20box%2C%20it's%20too%20small.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhy%20do%20cats%20need%20a%20large%20litter%20box%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECats%20need%20a%20large%20litter%20box%20to%20avoid%20stepping%20on%20soiled%20spots%20and%20comfortably%20dig%20and%20bury%20their%20waste.%20As%20mid-level%20predators%2C%20they%20have%20an%20instinct%20to%20hide%20their%20elimination%20from%20both%20potential%20prey%20and%20predators.%20Having%20a%20larger%20litter%20box%20with%20plenty%20of%20space%20between%20deposits%20allows%20them%20to%20bury%20their%20waste%20more%20effectively%2C%20says%20Johnson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20know%20if%20a%20litter%20box%20is%20too%20small%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20cat%20eliminates%20over%20the%20side%20of%20the%20litter%20box%2C%20perches%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20box%2C%20or%20leaves%20the%20box%20to%20cover%20their%20waste%2C%20they%20typically%20need%20a%20bigger%20box.%20When%20a%20litter%20box%20is%20too%20small%2C%20difficult%20to%20use%2C%20or%20dirty%2C%20a%20cat%20may%20choose%20to%20eliminate%20outside%20the%20litter%20box.%20According%20to%20Quandt%2C%20improper%20elimination%20(pooping%20and%20peeing%20outside%20the%20litter%20box)%20is%20a%20leading%20reason%20people%20surrender%20their%20cats%20to%20shelters%20or%20rehome%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20large%20cats%20use%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20use%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%20depends%20on%20your%20cat's%20age%20and%20any%20underlying%20health%20conditions.%20Top-entry%20litter%20boxes%20can%20be%20difficult%20or%20impossible%20for%20some%20cats%20to%20access%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20your%20cat%20has%20difficulty%20accessing%20their%20box%2C%20they're%20less%20likely%20to%20use%20it%2C%20Quandt%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3Cp%3EA%20litter%20box%20should%20be%20at%20least%201.5%20times%20the%20length%20of%20your%20cat%20from%20nose%20to%20tail%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.catbehaviorsolutions.org%2Fabout-molly%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMolly%20DeVoss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20specialist%20and%20founder%20of%20Cat%20Behavior%20Solutions.%20Your%20cat's%20body%20should%20not%20touch%20the%20sides%20while%20in%20the%20box.%20It's%20also%20important%20that%20all%20cats%20who%20use%20it%20can%20access%20it%20easily%2C%20and%20it%20should%20also%20be%20easy%20to%20clean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KittyGoHere%20checks%20all%20these%20boxes.%20DeVoss's%C2%A0cats%2C%20including%20a%20large%2017-inch%20long%20orange%20tabby%2C%20use%20this%20box%2C%20which%20she%20likes%20for%20its%20simplicity%20and%20large%20interior.%20Many%20cats%20favor%20a%20large%20litter%20box%20that%20feels%20natural%20to%20use%2C%20and%20a%20simplistic%20open%20design%20means%20no%20latches%2C%20hoods%2C%20or%20drawers%20to%20fuss%20with%20when%20cleaning%20the%20box.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2028%20inches%20long%20by%2022%20inches%20wide%2C%20this%20is%20the%20largest%20cat%20litter%20box%20we've%20seen.%20Even%20cats%20the%20size%20of%20Maine%20coons%20can%20comfortably%20enter.%20The%20design%20includes%20a%20low%20entry%20that's%203%20inches%20at%20its%20lowest%20point%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20box%20a%20great%20option%20for%20senior%20cats.%20Many%20cats%20over%2010%20years%20old%20have%20arthritis%2C%20so%20providing%20a%20li