%20both%20came%20forward%2C%20Trump%20feared%20for%20voters%2C%20not%20family%2C%20Pecker%20told%20jurors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20up%20popped%20a%20doorman%20with%20a%20tale%20%E2%80%94%20false%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20%E2%80%94%20of%20an%20illegitimate%20child.%20Then%2C%20in%20swift%20succession%20and%20with%20the%202016%20election%20just%20months%20away%2C%20a%20Playboy%20Bunny%20and%20a%20porn%20star%20appeared%20with%20more%20sex%20scandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20their%20decadeslong%20friendship%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20worried%20about%20his%20family%20hearing%20these%20kinds%20of%20unsavory%20stories%2C%20former%20National%20Enquirer%20publisher%20David%20Pecker%20told%20a%20Manhattan%20jury%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20months%20before%20the%202016%20election%2C%20all%20Trump%20worried%20about%20was%20his%20voters%2C%20Pecker%20testified%20on%20his%20third%20day%20on%20the%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrior%20to%20the%20election%2C%20if%20a%20negative%20story%20was%20coming%20out%20with%20respect%20to%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20and%20we%20spoke%20about%20it%2C%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20Melania%20and%20Ivanka%2C%20what%20the%20family%20might%20hear%20or%20say%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20publisher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pronounced%20the%20former%20first%20lady's%20name%2C%20%26quot%3BMillenia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%202016%20election%2C%20Pecker%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%20first%20Trump%20Tower%20doorman%20Dino%20Sajudin%2C%20then%20Playboy%20Bunny%20Karen%20McDougal%2C%20then%20porn%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels%20tried%20to%20sell%20their%20stories%20to%20the%20supermarket%20tabloid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20conversations%20with%20Mr.%20Trump%20about%20these%20stories%2C%20his%20family%20was%20never%20mentioned%2C%26quot%3B%20Pecker%20said%2C%20under%20direct%20examination%20by%20prosecutor%20Joshua%20Steinglass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20his%20concern%20was%20with%20the%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20Pecker%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20directing%20Pecker%20to%20describe%20Trump's%20priority%20of%20campaign%20over%20family%2C%20Steinglass%20was%20pursuing%20a%20legal%20point%2C%20not%20a%20moral%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20stories%20%E2%80%94%20doorman%2C%20bunny%2C%20and%20porn%20star%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20deep-sixed%20by%20the%20Enquirer%20as%20part%20of%20what%20Manhattan%20prosecutors%20call%20an%20illegal%20conspiracy%20to%20influence%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20falsified%2034%20Trump%20Organization%20business%20documents%20%E2%80%94%20invoices%2C%20checks%2C%20ledger%20entries%20%E2%80%94%20to%20disguise%20the%20%24130%2C000%20in%20hush%20money%20paid%20to%20Daniels%20just%2011%20days%20before%20the%20election%20as%20legal%20fees%20to%20then-attorney%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20prosecutors%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20falsifications%20are%20felonies%2C%20District%20Attorney%20Alvin%20Bragg%20has%20charged%2C%20because%20the%20%24130%2C000%20was%20actually%20an%20illegal%20campaign%20expenditure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20books%20were%20cooked%2C%20Bragg%20alleges%2C%20to%20hide%20an%20underlying%20campaign%20finance%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPecker%20and%20his%20top%20lieutenant%2C%20National%20Enquirer%20editor-in-chief%20Dylan%20Howard%2C%20knew%20that%20in%20catching%20and%20killing%20Trump's%20trio%20of%20sex%20scandals%2C%20they%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20contributing%20to%20his%20campaign%20in%20violation%20election%20law%2C%20Thursday's%20testimony%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPecker%20told%20jurors%20he%20had%20been%20investigated%20by%20California%20officials%20for%20just%20this%20sort%20of%20thing%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20before%20Trump's%202016%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20a%20similar%20catch-and-kill%20arrangement%20with%20Arnold%20Schwarzenegger%20in%20the%20runup%20to%20the%20star's%20successful%202003%20run%20for%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20number%20of%20women%20called%20up%20the%20National%20Enquirer%20about%20stories%20that%20they%20have%20to%20sell%20on%20different%20relationships%2C%20or%20contacts%2C%20and%20sexual%20harassments%2C%20that%20they%20felt%20that%20Arnold%20Schwarzenegger%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Pecker%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20deal%20I%20had%20with%20Arnold%20was%20that%20I%20would%20call%20him%20and%20acquire%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20these%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPecker%20told%20jurors%20that%20his%20publishing%20empire%2C%20American%20Media%20International%2C%20or%20AMI%2C%20was%20not%20charged%20with%20campaign%20finance%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20very%20embarrassing%20to%20me%20and%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20testified%20of%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20lieutenant%2C%20Howard%2C%20crossed%20his%20fingers%20extra%20hard%20on%20election%20night%2C%20a%20text%20message%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%20if%20he%20wins%2C%26quot%3B%20Howard%20texted%20a%20relative%20as%20Trump's%20electoral%20college%20votes%20rolled%20in%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20pardoned%20for%20electoral%20fraud.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20text%20was%20not%20shown%20to%20jurors%20after%20a%20successful%20challenge%20by%20the%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20said%20Howard%20is%20unable%20to%20appear%20as%20their%20witness%20because%20he%20is%20in%20Australia%20with%20a%20spinal%20injury.%20Defense%20lawyers%20complained%20they%20could%20not%20question%20Howard%20about%20the%20text%20if%20it%20were%20admitted%20as%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPecker's%20testimony%20continues%20Friday%20with%20cross-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20spent%20three%20days%20describing%20a%20secret%20and%20complex%20catch-and-kill%20infrastructure%20that%20spanned%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20both%20his%20tabloid%20empire%20and%20the%20Trump%20campaign%2C%20involving%20multiple%20attorneys%20and%20carefully%20worded%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDougal's%20August%205%2C%202016%2C%20catch-and-kill%20contract%20was%20%26quot%3Bbulletproof%26quot%3B%20after%20being%20reviewed%20by%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20attorney%2C%20Pecker%20said%2C%20in%20some%20of%20the%20most%20damaging%20testimony%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20calling%20the%20shots%2C%20though%20often%20from%20the%20shadows%2C%20using%20Cohen%20as%20an%20intermediary%2C%20the%20testimony%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKaren%20is%20a%20nice%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20Pecker%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202016%2C%20when%20McDougal%20surfaced%20as%20a%20scandal%20threat%2C%20claiming%20a%20nearly%20year-long%20affair%20with%20Trump%20from%20ten%20years%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20think%20I%20should%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20Pecker%2C%20who%20believed%20McDougal%20was%20telling%20the%20truth%2C%20said%20Trump%20asked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20should%20buy%20the%20story%20and%20take%20it%20off%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Pecker%20said%20he%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%20to%20me%20that%20Michael%20Cohen%20would%20be%20calling%20me%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Pecker%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGo%20ahead%20and%20buy%20the%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Pecker%20said%20Cohen%20soon%20told%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pecker%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWho's%20going%20to%20pay%20for%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20worry.%20I'm%20your%20friend.%20The%20boss%20will%20take%20care%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20who%20he%20understood%20%26quot%3Bthe%20boss%26quot%3B%20to%20be%2C%20Pecker%20answered%2C%20%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20wound%20up%20not%20reimbursing%20Pecker%20for%20McDougal's%20%24150%2C000%20non-disclosure%20agreement%2C%20the%20former%20tabloid%20executive%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20despite%20the%20so-