at%20Purdue%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20believe%20that%20the%20way%20we%20process%20and%20cook%20foods%20is%20going%20to%20disable%20most%20bacteria%20and%20viruses%2C%20including%20this%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPasteurization%20should%20kill%20H5N1%20in%20milk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22row%20of%20cows%20sticking%20their%20heads%20through%20metal%20bars%20to%20eat%20hay%20feed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a72620dfb1341e9ff1add%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20cow%20looks%20up%20from%20its%20feed%20at%20the%20Johann%20Dairy%20farm%20in%20Fresno%2C%20California.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Frandino%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20oversees%20the%20nation's%20milk%20supply%2C%20and%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20oversees%20dairy%20cows.%20Both%20say%20they%20believe%20the%20commercial%20milk%20supply%20is%20safe%2C%20due%20to%20the%20pasteurization%20process%20and%20the%20practice%20of%20disposing%20of%20milk%20from%20sick%20cows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasteurization%20heats%20milk%20at%20a%20high%20temperature%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20of%20time%20to%20kill%20microbes%20living%20inside%20it.%20Some%20states%20allow%20the%20sale%20of%20unpasteurized%2C%20aka%20%26quot%3Braw%2C%26quot%3B%20milk%20or%20cheese%2C%20which%20the%20CDC%20recommends%20avoiding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublic-health%20experts%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fhealth%2F2024%2F04%2F23%2Fbird-flu-virus-milk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F04%2F23%2Fhealth%2Fbird-flu-milk.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20they%2C%20too%2C%20believe%20pas