settled%20on%20a%20design%2C%20I%20started%20selecting%20colors.%20Polywood's%20online%20design%20tool%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20experiment%20with%20and%20see%20how%20different%20frame%20colors%20look%20with%20cushion%20colors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20narrowing%20down%20my%20selection.%20I%20eventually%20chose%20darker%20gray%20cushions%20that%20I%20thought%20would%20stand%20up%20to%20whatever%20my%20four%20children%20could%20throw%20at%20them%2C%20paired%20with%20a%20lighter%20gray%20frame.%20I%20like%20the%20contrast%20of%20two%20shades%20of%20gray%20that%20adds%20interest%20without%20being%20busy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20number%20of%20options%20available%20for%20frame%20and%20fabric%20pairings%20initially%20seemed%20overwhelming%2C%20I%20appreciated%20having%20options.%20Polywood%20will%20send%20fabric%20samples%20upon%20request.%20If%20I%20didn't%20have%20messy%20children%20at%20home%2C%20I%20might%20have%20picked%20one%20of%20the%20many%20beautiful%20patterns%20Polywood%20offers.%20However%2C%20since%20almost%20all%20the%20patterns%20have%20some%20white%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20take%20the%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20and%20versatility%20of%20the%20Acadia%20line%20work%20well%20for%20my%20family%20of%20six%20on%20my%20patio%20space%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20it%20would%20work%20well%20in%20most%20spaces.%20The%206-piece%20set%20can%20easily%20accommodate%20eight%20if%20we%20use%20the%20ottomans%20as%20seats.%20The%20set's%20chairs%2C%20ottomans%2C%20and%20table%20are%20light%20enough%20to%20move%20around%20to%20easily%20create%20different%20seating%20configurations%2C%20depending%20on%20if%20I%20want%20to%20lounge%20with%20my%20feet%20up%20or%20create%20more%20space%20for%20guests.%20I%20also%20really%20like%20that%20the%20set%20is%20customizable.%20If%20we%20need%20even%20more%20seating%2C%20I%20can%20order%20another%20couple%20of%20chairs%20instead%20of%20purchasing%20an%20entirely%20new%20set.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%20and%20Durability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224618%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20polywood%20chair%20and%20an%20ottoman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a8e800dfb1341e9ff364a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Acadia%20sofa%20and%20chairs%20are%20just%20as%20comfortable%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20than%20my%20living%20room%20sofa.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20old%20patio%20set%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20use%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20so%20I%20prioritized%20comfort%20when%20selecting%20a%20new%20set.%20I%20opted%20for%20Polywood's%20deep-seating%20line%20because%20I%20thought%20the%20design%20and%20plush%20cushions%20would%20work%20well%20for%20lots%20of%20lounging.%20Even%20though%20I%20expected%20the%20set%20to%20be%20comfortable%2C%20I%20was%20still%20stunned%20at%20how%20comfortable%20the%20set%20wound%20up%20being.%20My%20family%20has%20used%20the%20patio%20furniture%20for%20hours%20to%20have%20afterschool%20snacks%2C%20play%20board%20games%2C%20hang%20out%20with%20friends%2C%20and%20relax%20on%20the%20weekends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20children%20think%20the%20Polywood%20sofa%20is%20more%20comfortable%20than%20the%20one%20we%20have%20in%20our%20living%20room%2C%20and%20I%20agree.%20Multiple%20guests%20have%20used%20the%20set%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20remarked%20on%20how%20comfortable%20it%20is%20to%20use%20for%20longer%20periods%20of%20time.%20Seating%20cushions%20are%20just%20over%205%26quot%3B%20thick%2C%20and%20cushions%20that%20support%20the%20back%20are%20even%20more%20plush%20at%20about%206%26quot%3B%20thick.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20durable%20patio%20set%20was%20also%20something%20very%20important%20to%20me.%20My%20active%20kids%20can%20be%20rough%20on%20furniture%2C%20particularly%20outdoor%20furniture.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20live%20in%20the%20Mid-Atlantic%20region%20of%20the%20East%20Coast.%20My%20patio%20furniture%20must%20withstand%20hurricane-level%20rain%2C%20occasional%20hail%20storms%2C%20100%2B%20degree%20weather%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20snowstorms%2C%20and%20below-freezing%20temperatures%20in%20the%20winter.%20That's%20a%20tall%20order%20and%20past%20patio%20sets%20have%20shown%20significant%20wear%20and%20tear%20after%20just%20a%20year%2C%20even%20when%20I%20tried%20to%20be%20diligent%20about%20covering%20the%20sets%20when%20not%20in%20use.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20truly%20waterproof%20patio%20set%20was%20also%20a%20priority%20for%20me.%20I%20try%20to%20be%20diligent%20about%20covering%20my%20patio%20furniture%20when%20rain%20is%20in%20the%20forecast%20and%20often%20throw%20the%20cushions%20in%20the%20garage%20when%20particularly%20bad%20weather%20is%20expected.%20However%2C%20this%20doesn't%20always%20happen.%20Shortly%20after%20I%20received%20my%20Polywood%20set%2C%20it%20rained%20heavily%20for%20several%20days%20straight.%20I%20was%20really%20impressed%20with%20how%20well%20the%20cushions%20repelled%20water.%20I%20placed%20them%20vertically%20to%20dry.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20could%20tell%2C%20no%20water%20seeped%20beyond%20the%20fabric%20into%20the%20cushions.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20wanted%20a%20set%20that%20was%20as%20maintenance-free%20as%20possible.%20I%20like%20that%20Polywood%20is%20made%20of%20durable%20plastic%20that%20never%20requires%20staining%2C%20sanding%2C%20waterproofing%2C%20or%20painting.%20Polywood%20also%20applies%20a%20UV%20protectant%20and%20color%20throughout%20the%20recycled%20plastic%20used%20to%20construct%20furniture%2C%20so%20pieces%20should%20resist%20fading.%20The%20hardware%20Polywood%20uses%20to%20assemble%20the%20furniture%20is%20marine-grade%20quality%2C%20so%20it%20should%20not%20rust.%20I%20have%20found%20my%20Polywood%20set%20to%20be%20easy%20to%20clean.%20It's%20been%20easy%20to%20wipe%20off%20the%20frames%20with%20a%20cloth%20and%20water.%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20easily%20shake%20fallen%20leaves%20and%20crumbs%20off%20the%20cushions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20hoped%20that%20the%20cushion%20covers%20could%20be%20removed%20to%20be%20washed.%20Although%20covers%20can%20be%20removed%2C%20Polywood%20recommends%20vacuuming%20cushions%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.polywood.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F4421954481179-Cushion-or-Fabric-Care-Maintenance%3Fgad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCj0KCQjwlZixBhCoARIsAIC745CEyrb6Lcyf9YVA3n3-TBguEiy5Fc0OphtKWJtddpsqwM9q1BB8lAcaAhXFEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espot-cleaning%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20mild%20dish%20soap%20and%20water%20for%20cleaning.%20They%20also%20provide%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polywood.com%2Fblog%2Foutdoor-living%2Fhome-improvement%2Fhow-to-clean-outdoor-cushions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstructions%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20deep%20cleaning%20specific%20types%20of%20stains%2C%20such%20as%20bird%20droppings%20and%20red%20wine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESustainability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Polywood's%20most%20notable%20features%20is%20how%20environmentally%20friendly%20they%20are%20as%20a%20brand.%20High-quality%20furniture%20that%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20replaced%20regularly%20is%20good%20for%20the%20earth%2C%20but%20Polywood%20goes%20further%20in%20how%20it%20does%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolywood%20keeps%20sustainability%20at%20the%20core%20of%20its%20operations.%20They%20strive%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero%20waste%26quot%3B%20company%2C%20meaning%20that%20most%20furniture%20is%20made%20to%20order%2C%20so%20there%20are%20few%20or%20no%20unsold%20pieces%20sitting%20around.%20Moreover%2C%20not%20only%20is%20Polywood%20furniture%20made%20from%20recycled%20material%2C%20but%20the%20furniture%20they%20create%20is%20also%20recyclable.%20Most%20shavings%20or%20scraps%20that%20are%20left%20over%20once%20a%20furniture%20set%20is%20manufactured%20are%20swept%20up%20and%20re-introduced%20to%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20recycling%20process%20where%20it%20becomes%20part%20of%20new%20furniture.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20furniture%20is%20returned%2C%20most%20is%20broken%20down%20and%20re-introduced%20to%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20process%20to%20be%20turned%20into%20new%20items.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20downside%20to%20purchasing%20a%20Polywood%20patio%20set%20is%20the%20cost.%20However%2C%20having%20been%20through%20several%20less%20expensive%20patio%20sets%20that%20did%20not%20hold%20up%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20invested%20in%20a%20quality%20set%20from%20the%20beginning.%20I%20have%20probably%20spent%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20Polywood%20set%20on%20patio%20furniture%20that%20looked%20great%20initially%20but%20quickly%20looked%20shabby%20and%20fell%20apart.%20Having%20owned%20several%20patio%20sets%2C%20I%20could%20immediately%20tell%20the%20difference%20in%20quality%20and%20believe%20this%20set%20will%20be%20a%20great%20investment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20downside%20is%20the%20amount%20of%20cardboard%20I%20was%20left%20with%20after%20unpacking%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20white-glove%20delivery%20option%2C%20even%20if%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20one.%20However%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20Polywood's%20packing%20materials%20are%20recyclable%2C%20which%20softened%20the%20blow%20of%20so%20much%20trash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolywood's%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20means%20that%20most%20furniture%20is%20made-to-order.%20Although%20furniture%20is%20produced%20relatively%20quickly%2C%20most%20customers%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20wait%20several%20days%20or%20more%20for%20their%20furniture%20to%20arrive%2C%20even%20with%20%26quot%3Bquick%20ship%26quot%3B%20options.%20In%20the%20age%20of%20free%20two-day%20delivery%2C%20some%20customers%20may%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20wait.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20have%20been%20able%20to%20remove%20cushion%20covers%20for%20clearing.%20However%2C%20since%20Polywood%20recommends%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polywood.com%2Fblog%2Foutdoor-living%2Fhome-improvement%2Fhow-to-clean-outdoor-cushions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espot-cleaning%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20will%20follow%20those%20instructions%20to%20prolong%20their%20life.%20Polywood%20does%20sell%20replacement%20parts%20but%20does%20not%20list%20prices.%20I%20found%20it%20frustrating%20that%20it's%20impossible%20to%20find%20out%20how%20much%20a%20new%20cushion%20or%20cover%20costs%20without%20submitting%20a%20special%20request.%20I%20hope%20mine%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time%2C%20but%20it%20would%20still%20be%20nice%20to%20know%20how%20much%20I%20am%20looking%20at%20for%20a%20replacement%20if%20I%20need%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPolywood%20is%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20outdoor%20furniture%20that%20should%20last%20for%20years.%20It's%20also%20a%20very%20environmentally%20friendly%20choice.%20If%20an%20entire%20Polywood%20set%20is%20not%20in%20your%20budget%2C%20ordering%20a%20piece%20or%20two%20at%20a%20time%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20start%20building%20a%20collection%2C%20or%20opting%20for%20a%20less%20expensive%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMore%20options%20from%20Polywood%20to%20explore%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fpolywood-furniture-review-sofa-set%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714079768000%2C%22visual%22%3A%