st.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20came%20home%20in%20February%20and%20saw%20her%2017-year-old%2C%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20kitchen%20cooking%20something%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20incident%20occurred.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20always%20crafty%20and%20making%20things%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20think%20anything%20of%20it%20when%20I%20saw%20her%20at%20the%20stove.%20About%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20later%2C%20Allison%20said%20she%20had%20burnt%20herself.%20She%20showed%20me%20it%20and%20at%20first%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20paper%20towel%20but%20it%20was%20her%20skin%20that%20had%20peeled%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20daughter%20had%20been%20preparing%20the%20materials%20for%20an%20all-natural%20hair%20removal%20procedure%20called%20sugaring%20or%20sugar%20wax%2C%20which%20uses%20a%20solution%20of%20sugar%2C%20honey%2C%20and%20water%20instead%20of%20standard%20wax.%20The%20resulting%20material%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20applied%20to%20any%20region%20of%20the%20body%2C%20from%20the%20armpits%20to%20the%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20this%20method%20was%20initially%20created%20by%20the%20Egyptians%2C%20Ms%20Boles%20found%20it%20on%20TikTok%2C%20where%20it%20has%20become%20extremely%20popular.%20%26quot%3BThe%20original%20video%20just%20came%20up%20on%20her%20TikTok%20'for%20you'%20page.%20She%20hadn't%20been%20searching%20for%20it%20but%20after%20seeing%20the%20first%20video%20she%20searched%20for%20more%20on%20TikTok%20and%20then%20did%20some%20further%20research%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20tragedy%20struck%20when%20Ms%20Boles%20followed%20the%20directions%20in%20the%20video%2C%20which%20instructed%20her%20to%20put%20the%20glop%20in%20the%20refrigerator%20and%20reheat%20it%20in%20the%20microwave%20for%20a%20few%20hours.%20The%20hot%20wax%20allegedly%20splattered%20her%20thumb%20as%20she%20was%20stirring%20the%20mixture%20causing%20the%20sugar%20wax%20to%20pop.%20The%20wax%20was%20so%20hot%20that%20it%20ended%20up%20peeling%20her%20skin%20off%20when%20she%20ran%20to%20rinse%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20they%20reached%20the%20emergency%20room%20at%20a%20hospital%2C%20doctors%20stated%20that%20she%20was%20the%20second%20patient%20who%20came%20in%20with%20the%20same%20issue.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20Allison%20told%20the%20doctor%20what%20happened%20he%20said%20he%20had%20watched%20the%20TikTok%20videos%20and%20explained%20that%20by%20putting%20the%20hot%20wax%20into%20the%20fridge%20you%20are%20essentially%20flash%20cooling%20it.%20When%20the%20wax%20is%20in%20the%20fridge%20for%20only%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20it%20doesn't%20cool%20evenly%20which%20leaves%20hot%20pockets%20in%20the%20wax%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2046-year-old%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20put%20it%20in%20the%20microwave%20these%20pockets%20are%20then%20going%20to%20get%20even%20hotter%2C%20but%20the%20other%20bits%20of%20the%20wax%20will%20only%20get%20warm%20which%20causes%20a%20combustion%20reaction%20which%20pops%20the%20hot%20pockets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20then%20diagnosed%20by%20a%20doctor%20with%20a%20serious%20second-degree%20burn%2C%20which%20would%20take%20four%20weeks%20to%20recover.%20Ms%20Boles'%20mother%20worries%20that%20her%20half-baked%20effort%20at%20mane%20removal%20would%20leave%20her%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bpermanent%20scar%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20her%20skin%20has%20now%20grown%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Renken%20is%20urging%20TikTok%20to%20include%20disclaimers%20in%20its%20DIY%20cosmetics%20videos%20in%20light%20of%20the%20traumatic%20experience.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20with%20every%20DIY%20project%20video%20(on%20TikTok)%20there%20should%20be%20some%20parental%20consent%20or%20age%20recommendations%20on%20the%20video%20just%20like%20there%20are%20on%20toys.%20Allison%20was%20very%20upset%20and%20she%20feels%20that%20even%20though%20she%20did%20all%20her%20research%2C%20she%20has%20now%20heard%20other%20people%20getting%20burned%20(by%20sugar%20wax)%20why%20aren't%20they%20telling%20us%2C%20that%20you%20can%20get%20hurt.%20She%20feels%20deceived%20by%20all%20the%20videos%20and%20research%20she%20did%20(into%20sugar%20wax)%20as%20they%20all%20told%20her%20the%20same%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20representatives%20from%20TikTok%20asserted%20that%20because%20of%20the%20inherent%20danger%20of%20the%20activities%20shown%2C%20access%20to%20the%20content%20is%20limited%20to%20those%20above%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20They%20also%20stated%20that%20they%20included%20cautionary%20labels%20informing%20users%20of%20the%20potentially%20hazardous%20nature%20of%20these%20activities%20and%20that%20TikTok%20isn't%20the%20only%20site%20where%20videos%20of%20sugaring%20and%20other%20do-it-yourself%20beauty%20tips%20are%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714056060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fnpcopqpg_waxing_625x300_25_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-teen-left-with-severe-burns-scarring-after-trying-sugar-waxing-trend-5522567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mother%20said%20that%20her%20daughter's%20blister%20was%20%26quot%3Bbigger%20than%20her%20thumb%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20around%20three%20inches%20tall.%20%26quot%3BThen%20it%20popped%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-teen-left-with-severe-burns-scarring-after-trying-sugar-waxing-trend-5522567%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-teen-left-with-severe-burns-scarring-after-trying-sugar-waxing-trend-5522567%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-teen-left-with-severe-burns-scarring-after-trying-sugar-waxing-trend-