0the%20UPSC.%20Nevertheless%2C%20there%20were%20moments%20of%20disappointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20score%20well%20in%20my%20mock%20tests%20despite%20studying%20hard%20for%20them.%20It%20would%20feel%20disheartening.%20But%2C%20I%20began%20to%20tell%20myself%20that%20if%20it%20were%20seeming%20impossible%2C%20there%20was%20something%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20smart%20work%20rather%20than%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recalibration%20of%20the%20strategy%20followed%20by%20discussions%20with%20peers%20would%20usually%20prove%20effective.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20go%20through%20model%20answer%20sheets%2C%20check%20how%20toppers%20had%20approached%20tough%20questions%2C%20and%20then%20begin%20my%20preparation%20with%20a%20new%20mindset%2C%E2%80%9D%20Samyak%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20above%20all%2C%20follow%20your%20calling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETasting%20success%20in%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20meant%20all%20the%20more%20to%20Samyak%20who%20had%20found%20the%20courage%20to%20navigate%20this%20path%20after%20years%20of%20exposure%20to%20other%20professional%20fields.%20Following%20Class%2012%2C%20he%20began%20preparing%20for%20engineering%20but%20dropped%20out%20after%20his%20first%20year.%20He%20then%20pursued%20a%20BA%20in%20English%20Honors%20from%20Delhi%20University%20followed%20by%20journalism%20at%20the%20Institute%20of%20Mass%20Communication%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20Samyak%20began%20to%20get%20invested%20in%20current%20affairs%2C%20particularly%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20of%202019.%20Intent%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20mechanism%20creating%20change%20in%20society%2C%20Samyak%20decided%20to%20follow%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281857%2Fupsc-cse-interview-topper-ias-apala-m